name: Super Spaceball '93
overview: A two player Pong game, brought up to the times in this 1993 release. Featuring interesting space themed backgrounds a asteroid that bounces between the top and the bottom of the playing field, deflecting balls in unexpected ways and power ups and other surprises. The game was created by Anjam Sarwar and Mohammed Iqbal and was published on the Assassins CD02 Ultimate Games collection.
